isible. When you click on the comment text field it opens all other fields (Name, Email, Website, etc...). If you want to keep all fields open, please set this option "expended".'=>'默认情况下，仅评论文本字段可见。 当您单击评论文本字段时，它将打开所有其他字段（名称，邮箱，网站等...）。 若您希望所有字段保持打开状态，请将此项设置为“已展开”。','Comment Form View'=>'评论表单视图','COMMENT'=>'评论','We are sorry, you are not allowed to comment more than %d time(s)!'=>'抱歉，您发表评论的次数不得超过%d次！','Remove Vote Data'=>'删除投票数据','By default, comment date is displayed with the human readable format, such as [X days ago]. For some languages, you may need to change the sequence of words in this date. This option provides shordcodes for each word allowing you manage the order. [number] is the \'X\', [time_unit] is the \'days\', [adjective] is the \'ago\'.'=>'默认情况下，评论日期以人机友好的格式显示，如[X天前]。 对于一些语言，您可能需要更改此日期中的单词顺序。 此选项为每个单词提供短代码，使您可以管理顺序。 [number]是“ X”，[time_unit]是“ 天”，[adjective]是“ 前”。','Structure of Human Readable Date Format'=>'人机友好型日期格式结构','Once a question is added in article editor (backend), readers will see a small comment icon (call to leave a feedback) next to the text part you\'ve selected for your question on article (front-end). This icon calls people to leave a feedback, using the type you\'ve selected in this option. For example, if you\'ve chosen the "Blink" option, once reader scrolled  and reached to the article text with question, it animates with comment button size and color changes attracting readers attention.'=>'在文章编辑器（后端）中添加问题后，读者会在您为文章问题（前端）选择的文本部分旁边看到一个小评论图标（要求留下反馈）。 此图标会使用您在此选项中选择的类型来呼吁人们留下反馈。 例如，若您选择了“眨眼”选项，则当读者滚动并到达带有问题的文章文本时，它将通过评论按钮的大小和颜色变化进行动画处理，从而引起读者的注意。','Animation for "Leave a Feedback" button in article content'=>'文章内容中“留下反馈”按钮的动画','This filter button appears next to all filter buttons and comment sorting options. It allows to filter and display article inline feedbacks (comments made while reading current article).'=>'该过滤器按钮出现在所有过滤器按钮和评论排序选项旁边。它允许过滤和显示文章内联反馈（阅读当前文章时发表的评论）。','Display filter button to load inline feedbacks'=>'显示过滤器按钮以加载内联反馈','Inline Commenting'=>'内联评论','Bubble - Hide the invitation message in X seconds'=>'气泡-在X秒内隐藏邀请消息','In most cases article readers don\'t even think about leaving some comment. Using this option you can enable Bubble &laquo;Invite to Comment&raquo; message. Once page is loaded and visitor has read some content, it reminds about comments and calls to leave a reply.'=>'在多数情况下，文章的读者甚至不会考虑留下一些评论。使用此项，您可以启用气泡&raquo;邀请评论&raquo;消息。一旦页面被加载且访问者已经阅读了一些内容，它提醒评论且呼吁留下回复。','Bubble - Invite to comment in X seconds'=>'气泡-在X秒内邀请发表评论','If the Bubble live update is enabled, it shows new comments excerpts as a pop-up information to article reads in real-time. This keeps website visitors up to date and engages them join to the discussion.'=>'若启用了气泡实时更新，它将显示新评论摘录作为实时阅读文章的弹出信息。这样可以使网站访问者了解最新情况，并吸引他们加入讨论。','Bubble - Notify on New Comments'=>'气泡-通知新评论','Comment Bubble Live Update'=>'评论气泡实时更新','Comment Bubble is a real-time updating sticky comment icon on your web pages. It invites people to comment, displays current comments information and notifies current page viewers about new comments.'=>'评论气泡是您网页上的一个实时更新的固定评论图标。它邀请人们评论，显示当前评论信息，并通知当前页面访问者关于新评论。','Live Commenting and Notifications'=>'实时评论和通知','Once image is uploaded, it\'ll generate thumbnails according to your selected sizes. When you set up a new WordPress website, the platform gives you three image sizes to play with: thumbnail, medium, and large (plus the file\'s original resolution). You may have other options and sizes which are registered by current active theme and by other plugins.'=>'一旦图片被上传，它将根据您选择的尺寸生成缩略图。当您建立一个新WordPress站点时，该平台会为您提供三种图像尺寸供您使用：缩略图，中号和大号（加上文件的原始分辨率）。您可能还有其他选项和大小，这些选项和大小由当前启用的主题和其他插件注册。','Generate Thumbnail Sizes'=>'生成缩略图大小','Single Image Sizes in Comments'=>'评论中单个图片大小','Show Comments Media in Dashboard'=>'在仪表板中显示评论媒体','You can not set this value more than \'upload_max_filesize\' and \'post_max_size\'. If you want to increase server parameters please contact to your hosting service support.'=>'您不能将此值设置为超过“upload_max_filesize”和“post_max_size”。若您想增加服务器参数，请联系您的主机服务支持。','Max Uploaded Size'=>'最大上传尺寸','Allowed File Types'=>'允许文件类型','Enable Lightbox for Attached Images'=>'为附加图片启用灯箱','Allow Media Uploading for Guests'=>'允许访客上传媒体','This option allows commenters to attach an image with comments.'=>'此项允许评论者评论中附带图像。','Enable Media Uploading'=>'启用媒体文件上传','The number of words before breaking comment text (Read more)'=>'截断评论文本的字数（了解更多）','Image Source URL to Image Conversion'=>'图片源URL到图片转换','Comment Content and Media'=>'评论内容和媒体','This option allows control commenting activity per user. You can set maximum number of comments users can leave per post or sitewide. It also allow to set restriction for comments or for replies only.'=>'此选项允许对每个用户进行控件评论活动。您可设置每个文章或站点范围内用户可发表评论的最大数量。它还允许设置评论或仅回复的限制。','Limit Comments per User'=>'限制每个用户评论','Display comment editing Information'=>'显示评论编辑信息','Enable editing for replied comments'=>'启用编辑已回复评论','Comment Moderation'=>'评论审核','Display Comment Author Labels'=>'显示评论作者标签','User Labels and Badges'=>'用户标签和徽章','Keep checked the "Notify of new replies to this comment" option by default'=>'默认情况下保持勾选"通知对此评论的新回复"选项','Display "Notify of new replies to this comment" option in comment form'=>'在评论表单中显示"通知对此评论的新回复"选项','Subscription types in Subscription Bar drop-down'=>'订阅栏下拉菜单中的订阅类型','Send E-Mail Notification to Mentioned Users'=>'发送电子邮件通知给被提及的用户','This option allows mentioning users in comments using @nicename method. Mentioned users will get notification via email if the next option is enabled. To get an advanced user mentioning features and to be able mention comments by #CommentID, we recommend the %s addon.'=>'此选项允许使用@nicename方法在评论中提及用户。若启用了下一个选项，被提及的用户将通过电子邮件收到通知。为获得高级用户提及功能并能够通过#CommentID提及评论，我们建议使用%s插件。','Enable User Mentioning'=>'启用用户提及','Subscription and User Following'=>'订阅和用户关注','IMPORTANT: In case your theme uses old versions of Font-Awesome lib, you should not disable this this option. The theme old version doesn\'t support new version icons, thus some wpDiscuz icons might be lost.'=>'重要说明：若您的主题使用旧版Font-Awesome库，则不应禁用此项。旧版主题不支持新版图标，因此某些wpDiscuz图标可能会丢失。','Load Font Awesome css lib'=>'加载Font Awesome css库','Comment Text Size'=>'评论文本大小','Starting from wpDiscuz 7 you can choose the [ Off ] option of comment style. It\'ll remove most of wpDiscuz CSS code and allow you write your own CSS for custom comment styling.'=>'从wpDiscuz 7开始，您可以选择评论样式的[关]选项。它将删除大部分wpDiscuz CSS代码，并允许您编写自己的CSS以用于自定义评论样式。','Styles and Colors'=>'样式和颜色','Enable Sitewide Usage of Default Avatars'=>'启用默认头像的站点使用范围','Default Avatar Source URL for Guests'=>'游客默认头像源URL','Default Avatar Source URL for Users'=>'用户默认头像源URL','This option only related to avatars in comment system. For sitewide avatar control, please use WordPress native avatar settings in Dashboard > Settings > Discussions admin page.'=>'此选项仅与评论系统中的头像相关。对于站点范围的头像控制，请在仪表板>设置>讨论管理页面中使用WordPress本地头像设置。','Display Avatars'=>'显示头像','This allows users to see own voted comments.'=>'这允许用户看到自己的投票评论。','Highlight Voting Buttons for Voters'=>'高亮显示投票按钮','Enable down vote button (dislike)'=>'启用否决按钮（踩）','Comment Voting Result Mode'=>'评论投票结果模式','Voting Buttons Icon'=>'投票按钮图标','Show Comment Date'=>'显示评论日期','Show Comment Link'=>'显示评论链接','Comment Thread Features'=>'评论线程特性','Comments Pagination Type'=>'评论分页类型','By default child comments are sorted by oldest on top. Using this option you can revers child comments order and sort them by newest on top.'=>'默认情况下，子评论按“最旧”排序。使用此选项，您可颠倒子评论的顺序，并按“最新”对其进行排序。','Display Comment Sorting Options'=>'显示评论排序选项','Display "Hottest Comment Threads" filter button'=>'显示“热门评论线程“筛选按钮','Display "Most Reacted Comments" filter button'=>'显示“最具反响的评论”筛选按钮','Keep your page loading speed high by disabling comments loading. Once the page loading is complete, this option will initiate AJAX request and load comments without affecting page loading speed. Also, you can select the [View Comments] button option to allow visitors load comments manually whenever they want.'=>'通过禁用评论加载以保持较高的页面加载速度。页面加载完毕后，此项将启动AJAX请求并加载评论，而不会影响页面加载速度。另外，您可以选择[查看评论]按钮选项以允许访客在需要时手动加载评论。','Comment List Loading Type'=>'评论列表加载类型','Comment Thread Displaying'=>'评论主题显示','Aggregate rating schema is a code integrated with post rating HTML. This enables Google to feature your post ratings and attract customers with it. When searching the internet, people will see your posts search results with star ratings. Even though those results are not at the top of search engine results page, those sites caught people attention first.'=>'聚合评级架构是与后评级HTML集成的代码。这样一来，谷歌就能展示您的帖子评分，并以此吸引客户。在互联网上搜索时，人们会看到带有星级的您的帖子搜索结果。即使这些结果不在搜索引擎结果页面的顶部，这些网站还是首先引起了人们的注意。','Enable Aggregate Rating Schema'=>'启用综合评分架构','Article and Comment Rating'=>'文章和评论评分','Baidu Client Secret'=>'百度Client Secret','Baidu Client ID'=>'百度Client ID','Baidu Login Button'=>'百度登录按钮','QQ AppKey'=>'QQ AppKey','QQ AppID'=>'QQ AppID','QQ Login Button'=>'QQ登录按钮','WeChat Secret'=>'微信Secret','WeChat App ID'=>'微信App ID','WeChat Login Button'=>'微信登录按钮','Weibo App Secret'=>'微博App Secret','Weibo App Key'=>'微博App Key','Weibo Login Button'=>'微博登录按钮','Yandex Password'=>'Yandex密码','Yandex ID'=>'Yandex ID','Yandex Login Button'=>'Yandex登录按钮','WhatsApp Share Button'=>'WhatsApp分享按钮','LinkedIn Client Secret'=>'LinkedIn Client Secret','LinkedIn Client ID'=>'LinkedIn Client ID','LinkedIn Login Button'=>'LinkedIn登录按钮','Instagram App Secret'=>'Instagram App Secret','Instagram App ID'=>'Instagram App ID','Instagram Login Button'=>'Instagram登录按钮','WordPress Client Secret'=>'WordPress Client Secret','WordPress Client ID'=>'WordPress Client ID','WordPress Login Button'=>'WordPress登录按钮','Disqus Secret Key'=>'Disqus Secret Key','Disqus Public Key'=>'Disqus Public Key','Disqus Login Button'=>'Disqus登录按钮','Google Client Secret'=>'Google Client Secret','Google Client ID'=>'Google Client ID','X - Consumer Secret (API Secret)'=>'X-用户私钥(API私钥)','Facebook Application Secret'=>'Facebook Application Secret','Facebook Share Button'=>'Facebook分享按钮','Facebook Login Button'=>'Facebook登录按钮','Use Website URL as Profile URL'=>'使用网站网址作为个人资料网址','By default wpDiscuz adds a link with comment author avatar to the author profile page, you can disable this link using this option. However in case you use some plugin with User Profile page, you should keep this option enabled. wpDiscuz is well integrated with %s, BuddyPress and Ultimate Member profile builder plugins.'=>'默认情况下，wpDiscuz将带有评论作者头像的链接添加到作者资料页，您可使用此选项禁用此链接。然而，若您在“用户资料”页上使用某些插件，则应保持启用此选项。wpDiscuz与%s，BuddyPress和Ultimate Member个人资料构建器插件很好地集成在一起。','The "My Content & Settings" button is located in comment filter panel on top of all comments, right after the [X Comments] phrase. This button opens a pop-up window allowing commenters manage their content and settings.'=>'“我的内容和设置”按钮位于所有评论顶部的评论筛选面板中，紧接在[X评论]短语之后。此按钮将打开一个弹出窗口，允许评论者管理其内容和设置。','Show "Login" link on comment form'=>'在评论表单上显示“登录”链接','Display logged-in user name and logout link on comment form'=>'在评论表单上显示登录的用户名和退出登录链接','User Authorization and Profile Data'=>'用户授权和配置文件数据','Display on Subscription Form'=>'在订阅表单上显示','Enable for Logged-in Users'=>'启用登录用户','Enable for Guests'=>'为游客启用','Request Method'=>'请求方法','reCAPTCHA Language'=>'reCAPTCHA 语言','reCAPTCHA Theme'=>'reCAPTCHA类型','Site Key'=>'站点密钥','Please click on buttons to disable or enable. The enabled buttons are colored green, the disabled buttons are gray. If you want to disable the whole formatting toolbar, please click on the [Disable formatting buttons] button. Options to manage Image Attachment button are located in \'Comment Content and Media\' setting page.'=>'请点击按钮以禁用或启用。启用的按钮显示为绿色，禁用的按钮显示为灰色。若要禁用整个格式化工具栏，请单击[禁用格式化按钮]按钮。管理“图像附件”按钮的选项位于“评论内容和媒体”设置页中。','Rich Editor Toolbar Buttons'=>'富文本编辑器工具按钮','Search engines rank web pages for mobile devices totally different. For the mobile devices, there are more restrictions for JS and CSS files loading. This is the main reason why wpDiscuz disables the Rich Editor for mobile devices by default. It\'s only enabled for desktop. If you have good cache and website optimizer plugins you can enable the rich editor for mobile devices as well.'=>'搜索引擎对移动设备网页的排名完全不同。对于移动设备，JS和CSS文件加载有更多限制。这是 wpDiscuz默认禁用移动设备富文本编辑器的主要原因。它仅适用于桌面。若您有良好的缓存和网站优化器插件，您也可为移动设备启用富文本编辑器。','Load Rich Editor'=>'加载富文本编辑器','wpDiscuz uses WordPress functions to keep guest Name, Email and Website information in cookies. Those are used to fill according fields of comment form on next commenting time. Set this option value -1 to make it unlimited. Set this option value 0 to clear those data when user closes browser.'=>'wpDiscuz使用WordPress功能将访客名称、邮箱和网站信息保存在cookie中。这些用于在下一次评论时根据评论表填写字段。将此项值设置为-1使其不受限制。将此项值设置为0可在用户关闭浏览器时清除这些数据。','Please synchronize comment data for the best performance and fastest experience'=>'请同步评论数据以获得最佳性能和最快体验','Comments votes data need to be regenerated'=>'评论票数数据需要重新生成','Closed Comments data need be regenerated'=>'关闭评论数据需要重新生成','Comment votes meta data need to be regenerated'=>'评论票数元数据需要重新生成','Jetpack Comments are active.'=>'Jetpack评论是活跃的。','Go to Installation Wizard &raquo;'=>'进入安装向导&raquo;','Go to Update Wizard &raquo;'=>'进入更新向导&raquo;','Please complete required steps to start using wpDiscuz 7'=>'请完成所需的步骤以开始使用wpDiscuz 7','Adds Invisible reCAPTCHA on all comment forms. Stops spam and bot comments with reCAPTCHA version 3'=>'在所有评论表单上添加不可见的reCAPTCHA。使用reCAPTCHA V3以停止垃圾邮件和机器人评论','Phrases Imported Successfully!'=>'短语已成功导入！','You do not have sufficient permissions to perform this action'=>'您没有足够的权限执行此操作','Sorry, uploading not allowed for this post'=>'抱歉，此文章不允许上传','Post ID not exists'=>'文章ID不存在','File is empty. Please upload something more substantial. This error could also be caused by uploads being disabled in your php.ini or by post_max_size being defined as smaller than upload_max_filesize in php.ini.'=>'文件为空。请上传更重要的内容。此错误也可能是由于您的php.ini文件中的上传功能被禁用或post_max_size文件大小小于php.ini文件中的upload_max_filesize所导致。','Maximum post size is'=>'文章字数上限','Maximum upload file size is'=>'最大上传文件大小','Maximum number of uploaded files is'=>'上传文件的最大数量为','Not allowed file type'=>'不允许的文件类型','Are you sure you want to delete this attachment?'=>'您确定要删除此附件吗？','Would love your thoughts, please comment.'=>'希望看到您的想法，请您发表评论','Commenting is closed!'=>'评论已关闭！','Hi [MENTIONED_USER_NAME]!<br/>You have been mentioned in a comment posted on "[POST_TITLE]" post by [COMMENT_AUTHOR].<br/><br/>Comment URL: <a href="[COMMENT_URL]">[COMMENT_URL]</a>'=>'[MENTIONED_USER_NAME]，您好<br/>[COMMENT_AUTHOR]在“[POST_TITLE]”文章上已发表的评论中提及了您。<br/> <br/>评论URL：<a href="[COMMENT_URL]"> [COMMENT_URL] </a>','You have been mentioned in comment'=>'您在评论中被提及','All wpDiscuz addons are being developed by wpDiscuz developers at gVectors Team. These addons help us to keep top level development of the free wpDiscuz plugin. All essential and even dozens of extra-cool features are already available for free in the core wpDiscuz plugin. There are not any limits, any pro and paid versions of wpDiscuz. We have another dozens of awesome features in our to-do list which will be added for free in the future releases.'=>'所有wpDiscuz插件都是由gVectors团队的wpDiscuz开发人员开发的。这些插件帮助我们保持免费wpDiscuz插件的顶级开发。在核心的wpDiscuz插件中已经可以免费获得所有必需的甚至几十个超酷的功能。在任何专业版和付费版的wpDiscuz中没有任何限制。我们的待办事项列表中还有几十个极好的功能，这些功能将在未来的版本中免费添加。','Reset All Options'=>'重置所有选项','Reset Tab Options'=>'重置Tab选项','Back'=>'返回','Addons Settings'=>'插件设置','Open Settings'=>'打开设置','Find an option...'=>'查找选项…','Start Using wpDiscuz'=>'开始使用wpDiscuz','Thank You!'=>'谢谢您！','Next Step &raquo;'=>'下一步&raquo;','Finish Installation'=>'完成安装','Finish Update'=>'完成更新','Before, you had to create a Rating field in comment form to allow users rate article while they post a comment, there was no way to rate without commenting. Now you can allow users rate your articles without leaving a comment. wpDiscuz 7 has a built-in Article Rating system which is not based on comment form custom fields and appears on top of comment section, under the article content.'=>'在之前，您必须在评论表单中创建“评分”字段，以允许用户在他们发表评论时对文章进行评分，而不评论就无法进行评分。现在，您可允许用户在无需发表评论时对您的文章进行评分。wpDiscuz 7具有一个内置的“文章评分”系统，该系统不基于评论表单自定义字段，而是显示在文章内容下方、评论区顶部。','Enable Article Rating'=>'启用文章评分','Article Rating vs Comment Rating'=>'文章评分与评论评分','Select a part of text, add inline commenting form in post content using the green &laquo;Comment&raquo; button on post editor toolbar. Once it\'s added in article editor (backend), on article (front-end) readers will see a small comment icon next to the text part you\'ve selected.'=>'选择文本的一部分，在文章内容中使用绿色的&laquo;评论&raquo;添加内联的评论形式。按钮后编辑器工具栏。一旦它被添加到文章编辑器(后端)，文章(前端)的读者将看到一个小评论图标旁边的文本部分你已经选择。','Great News! Now you can add questions for readers on certain part of article content and ask for feedback while visitors read it.'=>'好消息！现在您可在文章内容的某些部分为读者添加问题，并在访客阅读文章时征求反馈。','Ask questions to readers and discuss directly on article content!'=>'向读者提问，直接就文章内容进行讨论！','Add Inline Commenting forms in article!'=>'在文章中添加内联评论表单！','Increase Your Comments!'=>'增加您的评论！','More News'=>'更多新闻','Comment Bubble Location'=>'评论气泡位置','Bubble Live Update'=>'气泡实时更新','The Bubble is also designed to invite article readers to comment. It displays invite message allowing them fast and easy jump to comment area.'=>'这个气泡也是用来邀请文章读者评论的。它显示邀请消息，使他们可以快速轻松地跳转到评论区域。','Comment Bubble is a sticky comment icon on your web pages. It keeps article readers and commenters up to date. It displays new comments as pop-up information or as a number in an orange circle.'=>'评论气泡是您网页上的固定评论图标。它使文章的读者和评论者保持最新。它以弹出信息或橙色圆圈中的数字形式显示新评论。','Comment Bubble'=>'评论气泡','Comments Layout #3'=>'评论布局#3','Comments Layout #2'=>'评论布局#2','Comments Layout #1'=>'评论布局#1','Layout #3'=>'布局#3','Layout #2'=>'布局#2','Layout #1'=>'布局#1','Choose Your Comments Layout'=>'选择您的评论布局','Comments Style'=>'评论样式','Comments Style & Layout'=>'评论样式和布局','To downgrade wpDiscuz, you should deactivate and delete wpDiscuz 7 plugin. Then download the previous 5.3.2 version ZIP file from wpDiscuz plugin page (use dropdown menu under statistic graphics). And install the ZIP file in Dashboard > Plugins > Add Plugin admin page. The downgrading is only recommended to gain a time to do template customizations or wait for help from our support team. Once the issues are resolved, you should update to latest wpDiscuz version.'=>'要降级wpDiscuz，您应停用并删除wpDiscuz 7插件。然后从wpDiscuz插件页面下载以前的5.3.2版本的ZIP文件（使用统计图形的下拉菜单）。并在仪表盘>插件>添加插件管理页面中安装ZIP文件。降级仅建议获取时间以进行模板自定义或等待我们支持团队的帮助。一旦解决问题，您应更新到最新的wpDiscuz版本。','I want to downgrade to previous 5.x version!'=>'我想降级到以前的5.x版本！','All problems displayed above have fixing tips in the same boxes. If, for some reason you can\'t solve those problems, we\'re ready to help you and fix those as soon as possible. Please open a support topic at gVectors support forum or contact as via support@gvectors.com email address. Our support team works from 6am till 6pm in GMT+0 timezone. Please be patient when you open a new support topic or when contacting us via email. We\'ll get back to you within 3-12 hours.'=>'上述所有问题在同一模块中都有修复提示。若您由于某些原因无法解决这些问题，我们已准备好为您提供帮助并尽快解决这些问题。请在gVectors支持论坛中打开支持话题，或通过support@gvectors.com电子邮件地址与我们联系。我们的支持团队在早6点到晚6点（GMT+0时区）工作。当您创建新支持话题或通过电子邮件与我们联系时，请您耐心等待。我们会在3到12个小时内与您联系。','I can\'t resolve the problems!'=>'我无法解决问题！','Use the "Deactivate" button located next to the "Learn More" button. Just click on this button and Jetpack Comments will be deactivated. Once it\'s disabled, please delete all caches.'=>'使用“了解更多”按钮旁“停用”按钮。仅需点击此按钮，Jetpack评论将被停用。一旦被停用，请删除所有缓存。','Please disable Jetpack Comments.'=>'请禁用Jetpack评论。','Jetpack Comments doesn\'t allow wpDiscuz comment form to be loaded on your posts and pages. It overwrites wpDiscuz Comment form.'=>'Jetpack评论不允许将wpDiscuz评论表单加载到您的文章和页面上。它会覆盖wpDiscuz评论表单。','Jetpack comments is active, please deactivate!'=>'Jetpack评论处于启用状态，请停用！','Ok, I understood'=>'好的，我明白','Prior to the wpDiscuz 7 release, we\'ve released new versions of all wpDiscuz addons. If you\'ve already using the latest versions, just activate those back. If your license key is expired and you cannot update, please renew those addons at gVectors Store with 30% discount applied automatically at checkout page. Just make sure you\'re logged-in in the store with your customer account.'=>'在wpDiscuz 7发行之前，我们已经发布了所有wpDiscuz附加组件的新版本。若您已经在使用最新版本，只需将其激活即可。若您的许可证密钥已过期且无法更新，请在gVectors商店续费那些插件，并在结帐页面自动享受30％的折扣。仅需确保您登录商店时，使用您的客户账户即可。','Please update wpDiscuz addons in Dashboard > Plugins admin page, then activate those back.'=>'请在仪表盘>插件管理页面中更新wpDiscuz插件，然后将其激活。','All old versions of addons are not compatible with wpDiscuz 7, because of new comment layouts and template functions. In order to avoid errors wpDiscuz deactivates those during the update process.'=>'由于新评论布局和模板功能，所有旧版本的插件均与wpDiscuz 7不兼容。为避免错误，wpDiscuz在更新过程中将其停用。','All wpDiscuz Addons are Deactivated!'=>'所有wpDiscuz插件均已停用！','Mark as solved'=>'标记为已解决','Use FTP client or hosting service cPanel > File Manager tool. WordPress theme folders are located in /wp-content/themes/ directory. The active theme folder can be detected by name.'=>'使用FTP客户端或托管服务cPanel>文件管理器工具。WordPress主题文件夹位于/wp-content/themes/目录中。可按名称检测已激活的主题文件夹。','Please remove wpDiscuz template files from your active theme\'s /wpdiscuz/ folder.'=>'请从启用主题的/wpdiscuz/文件夹中删除wpDiscuz模板文件。','Fix the problem: '=>'解决的问题：','Your customized wpDiscuz template files are no longer compatible with wpDiscuz 7.  This is a doable major version update (from 5.x to 7.x) with totally redesigned comment system and template files. You can do the same customization on the new wpDiscuz 7 template files with the same upgrade-safe way in case the new comment layouts don\'t fit your needs. Please find those below.'=>'您自定义的wpDiscuz模板文件不再与wpDiscuz 7兼容。这是可行的主要版本更新（从5.x到7.x），具有完全重新设计的评论系统和模板文件。若新的评论布局不符合您的需求，您可使用相同的升级安全方式对新的wpDiscuz 7模板文件进行相同的自定义。请在下面找到这些。','Information: '=>'信息：','Custom wpDiscuz template files are detected!'=>'自定义wpDiscuz模板文件被检测到！','Step 3'=>'步骤 3','Step 2'=>'步骤 2','Step 1'=>'步骤 1','Just 3 Steps to Complete Installation!'=>'仅需3个步骤即可完成安装！','Just 3 Steps to Complete Update!'=>'仅需3个步骤即可完成更新！','Backup Phrases'=>'备份短语','Rebuild Ratings'=>'重建评分','Start Rebuild'=>'开始重建','Fix Tables'=>'修复表','Regenerate Vote Data'=>'重新生成投票数据','Regenerate Closed Comments'=>'重新生成已关闭的评论','Import Phrases'=>'导入短语','Here you can import and restore wpDiscuz phrases. You just need to choose backup file and click import phrases.'=>'在这您可导入和恢复wpDiscuz短语。您仅需选择备份文件，然后点击导入短语。','Start Sync'=>'开始同步','Synchronize Commenters Data'=>'同步评论数据','Start Regenerate'=>'开始重新生成','Regenerate Vote Metas'=>'重新生成投票元','We love your reviews. This is the best way to say thank you to developers and support team.'=>'我们喜欢您的评论。这是对开发人员和支持团队表示感谢的最佳方式。','Leave a Good Review'=>'留下好评','Just log in to the translation platform with your WordPress.org account, and suggest translations.'=>'仅需用您的wordpress.org帐户登录到翻译平台，然后提出翻译建议。','We\'d really appreciate if you could help translating wpDiscuz to your language.'=>'若您能帮助将wpDiscuz翻译为您的语言，我们将非常感谢。','Help to Translate wpDiscuz'=>'帮助翻译wpDiscuz','Contribute'=>'贡献','Get all wpDiscuz premium addons with unlimited site license and save 90% with'=>'获得具有无限站点许可的所有wpDiscuz高级插件，并节省90％的费用','wpDiscuz Plugin Page'=>'wpDiscuz插件页','wpDiscuz Addons Support'=>'wpDiscuz插件支持','wpDiscuz Support'=>'wpDiscuz支持','wpDiscuz Demo'=>'wpDiscuz演示','Support & Community'=>'支持和社区','Privacy and GDPR'=>'隐私和GDPR','Translation'=>'翻译','Plugin Customization'=>'插件定制','Manage Comment Layout'=>'管理评论布局','Manage Comment Forms'=>'管理评论表单','Getting Started'=>'开始','Credits'=>'积分','Active Users and Guests'=>'活跃用户和游客','All Time'=>'所有时间','Last Year'=>'去年','Last 6 Months'=>'过去6个月','Last Month'=>'上个月','Last Week'=>'上周','Inline feedbacks'=>'内联反馈','All comments'=>'所有评论','Comment Statistic'=>'评论统计','Guest Commenters'=>'游客评论','User Commenters'=>'用户评论','All Comments'=>'所有评论','Overview & Comments Statistic'=>'概述和评论统计','Before, you had to create a Rating field in comment form to allow users rate article while they post a comment, there was no way to rate without commenting. Now you can allow users rate your articles without leavening a comment. wpDiscuz 7 has a built-in Post Rating system which is not based on comment form custom fields. You can see that on top of comment section like the left one on the screenshot below:'=>'在之前，您必须在评论表单中创建“评分”字段，以允许用户在发表评论时对文章进行评分，而不评论就无法进行评分。现在，您可允许用户无需发表评论就对您的文章进行评分。wpDiscuz 7具有内置的文章评分系统，该系统不基于评论表单的自定义字段。您可在评论区顶部看到它，就像下面左侧的屏幕截图中一样：','wpDiscuz comes with built-in social login and share buttons. It includes Facebook, X, Google, Disqus, WordPress.org, VK and OK Social Networks. You can enable those by managing API Keys in wpDiscuz > Settings > Social Login and Share options.'=>'wpDiscuz内置了社交登录和分享按钮。它包括Facebook、X、Google、Disqus、WordPress.org、VK和OK社交网络。您可通过在wpDiscuz>设置>社交登录和共享选项中管理API密钥来启用这些密钥。','The &laquo;Layout #1&raquo; is the simplest and cleanest layout. The &laquo;Layout #2&raquo; is designed for narrow comment sections. It displays comment content in wider area. The &laquo;Layout #3&raquo; layout is designed to accent comment thread hierarchy by colored vertical lines and indents.'=>'“布局#1”是最简单、最干净的布局；“布局#2”是为狭窄的评论部分设计的，它在更大的范围内显示评论内容；“布局#3”旨在通过彩色垂直线和缩进强调评论线程层次。','Comment Layout #3'=>'评论布局#3','Comment Layout #2'=>'评论布局#2','Comment Layout #1'=>'评论布局#1','wpDiscuz comment system design is totally changed. It comes with three nice layouts. You can even choose different layout for different pages. Three attractive, modern and clean layouts are ready to use. You can choose your proffered layout in wpDiscuz > Forms > Edit Comment Forms screen. Once the layout is changed, don\'t forget to delete all caches. Comment layouts are called simply &laquo;Layout #1&raquo;, &laquo;Layout #2&raquo;, &laquo;Layout #3&raquo;.'=>'wpDiscuz评论系统设计完全改变。它有三种漂亮的布局。您甚至可为不同页面选择不同的布局。三个吸引人、现代和干净的布局正准备使用。您可以在wpDiscuz>表单>编辑评论表单屏幕中选择您提供的布局。一旦布局被改变，别忘记删除全部缓存。评论布局被简单地称为布局#1、布局#2、布局#3。','If there is no new comments while visitor read the article, in most cases they don\'t even think about leaving some comment. The Bubble helps here too, it calls article readers to join to the discussion displaying them invite message. This message attracting readers attention and allows them fast and easy jump to comment area. Once page is loaded and visitor has read some content, it reminds about comments and calls to leave a reply.'=>'若访客在阅读文章时无新评论，则在大多数情况下，他们甚至不考虑发表评论。气泡在这里也有帮助，它呼吁文章读者加入讨论并向他们显示邀请消息。该消息吸引了读者的注意，并允许他们快速轻松地跳转到评论区域。一旦页面被加载且访问者阅读了一些内容后，它会提醒评论且呼吁留下回复。','Once new comment is posted, Bubble shows pop-up message with the new comment excerpt as it\'s shown on screenshot. The small &laquo;Reply&raquo; button allows to reply that comment immediately or readers can click on the pop-up notification and jump to that comment thread below the article. Just make sure the Bubble Live Update is enabled in wpDiscuz > Settings > Live Commenting and Notifications options.'=>'发表新评论后，气泡会显示弹出消息，其中包含新评论摘要，如屏幕截图所示。小号“回复”按钮允许立即回复评论，或读者可点击弹出的通知并跳转到文章下面的评论主题。仅需确保在wpDiscuz>设置>实时评论和通知选项中启用实时气泡更新。',' In wpDiscuz 7 the real-time commenting becomes more live and attractive. It\'s based on REST API and doesn\'t overload your server. A specific sticky comment icon on your web pages, called &laquo;Bubble&raquo; keeps article readers and commenters up to date. It can display new comments as pop-up notification or as number in an orange circle.'=>'在wpDiscuz 7中，实时评论变得更加生动和吸引人。它基于REST API，不会使服务器过载。在你的网页上有一个特殊的粘性评论图标，叫做&laquo;气泡&raquo;保持文章读者和评论者的最新信息。它可以将新的评论显示为弹出通知或橙色圆圈中的数字。','Live Notification / Bubble'=>'实时通知/气泡','The number of already left feedbacks will be displayed next to the feedback icon allowing people click and read other\'s feedbacks in the same place. Also, those feedbacks will be displayed with other standard comments in article comment section below.'=>'已留下的反馈数量将显示在反馈图标旁，使人们可在同一位置点击并阅读其他人的反馈。同样，这些反馈将与其他标准评论一起显示在下面的文章评论区。','Once a question is added in article editor (backend), on article (front-end), readers will see a small comment icon next to the text part you\'ve selected. This feature engages post readers inviting them comment and leave a feedback without scrolling down and using the standard comment form. Thus they leave reply and react to post content or questions during the reading process.'=>'在文章编辑器（后端），文章（前端）中添加问题后，读者会在所选文本部分旁边看到一个小评论图标。此功能可以吸引文章读者，邀请他们发表评论并留下反馈，而无需向下滚动并使用标准评论表单。因此，他们在阅读过程中留下答复并对文章内容或问题做出反应。','First time in blog commenting experience we introduce, the Inline Feedback feature. This is an interactive article reading option with questions and feedback. Now article authors can add some questions for readers on certain part of article content and ask for feedback while visitors read it.'=>'我们首次引入博客评论体验，即在线反馈功能。这是具有问题和反馈的交互式文章阅读选项。现在，文章作者可以在文章内容的某些部分为读者添加一些问题，并在访问者阅读文章时征求反馈。','Article Inline Feedback'=>'文章内联反馈','Article Rating vs Rating Field'=>'文章评分与评分字段','Social Login and Commenting'=>'社交登录和评论','Comment Layouts'=>'评论布局','Live Notification, Bubble!'=>'实时通知，气泡！','Inline Feedback'=>'内联反馈','What\'s New'=>'最新消息','It\'s totally improved with brand new innovative features bringing live to your website and discussions.'=>'全新的创新功能完全改善了您的网站和讨论的实时性。','This version is mostly focused on website visitors engagement,'=>'此版本主要侧重于网站访问者的参与度，','wpDiscuz 7 is a revolution in WordPress commenting experience.'=>'wpDiscuz 7是WordPress评论体验的一场革命。','Thank you for installing wpDiscuz!'=>'感谢您安装wpDiscuz！','Built to Engage'=>'专为参与而打造','Welcome to wpDiscuz 7'=>'欢迎使用wpDiscuz 7','Change the attached image'=>'更改附件图像','Attach an image to this comment'=>'将图像附加到此评论','Message if post size is bigger than allowed'=>'若文章大小大于允许值的消息','Message if upload file size is bigger than allowed'=>'若上传文件大小大于允许值的消息','Message if attached more files than allowed'=>'若附件数量超过允许值的消息','Message if one or more file types are not allowed'=>'若不允许的一种或多种文件类型的消息','Alert message before deleting attached file'=>'删除附件前的警告消息','Media Upload Phrases'=>'媒体文件上传短语','Awaiting for approval'=>'等待批准','Mentioned email content'=>'被提及时电子邮件内容','Mentioned email subject'=>'被提及时电子邮件主题','Inline Comments'=>'内联评论','You\'re not allowed to rate here'=>'您无法在此处评分','You cannot rate again'=>'您无法再次评分','Spoiler Title'=>'含有剧透的标题','Manage Comment'=>'管理评论','Reply to'=>'回复给','Last edited %1$s by %2$s'=>'最后由%2$s编辑于%1$s','Please login to comment'=>'请登录后发表评论','Inline Feedbacks'=>'内联反馈','View all comments'=>'查看所有评论','Your Email'=>'您的电子邮件地址','Your Name*'=>'您的姓名*','Notify me via email when a new reply is posted'=>'当有新回复时通过电子邮件通知我','Your comment here...'=>'您在此处的评论...','We are sorry, you are not allowed to create a new comment thread more than %d time(s)'=>'抱歉，您创建新评论线程的次数不得超过%d次','votes'=>'投票数','vote'=>'投票','Would love your thoughts, please comment'=>'希望看到您的想法，请您发表评论','Commenting is closed'=>'评论已关闭','Thank you for your feedback'=>'感谢您的反馈','Feedback on post content'=>'对文章内容的反馈','Please leave a feedback on this'=>'请对此提供反馈','Ask for Feedback'=>'要求反馈','Select a part of text and ask readers for feedback (inline commenting)'=>'选择一部分文字并要求读者提供反馈（内嵌评论）','Copied to clipboard!'=>'复制到剪贴板!','Share On WhatsApp'=>'分享到WhatsApp','Maintenance'=>'维护','Display [View Comments] button'=>'显示[查看评论]按钮','Display [View Comments] button to load comments manually'=>'显示[查看评论]按钮以手动加载评论','Initiate AJAX loading after page'=>'在页面后启动AJAX加载','Initiates AJAX loading once page loading is complete'=>'页面加载完成后启动AJAX加载','Load with page'=>'载入页面','Here you can find all necessary options to control comment threads loading, displaying and sorting functions. Using "Comment List Loading Type", "Comments Pagination Type" and "Display only parent comments" options, you can get the highest page loading speed.  Also you can manage comment thread filtering buttons.'=>'在这您可找到所有必要的选项以控制评论线程加载、显示和排序功能。使用“评论列表加载类型”，“评论分页类型”和“仅显示父评论”选项，可得到最快的页面加载速度。您还可管理评论线程筛选按钮。','Open the Feedback Form on scroll'=>'在滚动条上打开反馈表','Animate (blink and wiggle)'=>'动画（闪烁和摆动）','Once a question is added in article editor (backend), on article (front-end) readers will see a small comment icon next to the text part you\'ve selected. This feature engages post readers inviting them comment and leave a feedback while reading without scrolling down and using the standard comment form.'=>'在文章编辑器（后端）中添加问题后，在文章（前端）上，读者将在您选择的文本部分旁边看到一个小评论图标。此功能吸引文章读者邀请他们发表评论并在阅读时留下反馈，而无需向下滚动和使用标准评论表单。','You can add Inline Feedback button in post content using &laquo;Comment&raquo; button on post editor toolbar.'=>'您可以使用编辑器工具栏上的“评论”按钮在文章内容中添加内联反馈按钮。','Article Inline Feedback feature is an interactive article reading option with author\'s questions and readers feedback (comments). Now article authors can add some questions for readers on certain part of article content and ask for feedback while visitors read it.'=>'文章在线反馈功能是一种交互式的文章阅读选项，其中包含作者的问题和读者的反馈（评论）。现在，文章作者可以在文章内容的某些部分为读者添加一些问题，并在访问者阅读文章时征求反馈。','Right Corner'=>'右上角','Left Corner'=>'左上角','Content Left'=>'内容左侧','You can enabled comments live update without the Bubble too. There is a separate live update option to keep comment list real-time updating.'=>'您也可以启用实时评论更新，而无需气泡。有一个单独的实时更新选项，可以使评论列表实时更新。','This Bubble is also designed to invite article readers to comment. It displays invite message allowing them fast and easy jump to comment area.'=>'此气泡还旨在邀请文章读者发表评论。它显示邀请消息，使他们可以快速轻松地跳转到评论区。','In wpDiscuz 7 the real-time commenting becomes more live and attractive. It\'s based on REST API and doesn\'t overload your server. A specific sticky comment icon on your web pages, called &laquo;Bubble&raquo; keeps article readers and commenters up to date. It displays new comments as pop-up information or as a number in an orange circle.'=>'在wpDiscuz 7中，实时评论变得更加生动和吸引人。它基于REST API，不会使服务器负载。在你的网页上有一个特殊的固定评论图标，叫做气泡&raquo;保持文章读者和评论者的最新信息。它将新评论显示为弹出信息或橙色圆圈中的数字。','Layout Components'=>'布局组件','Comment Voting Buttons'=>'评论投票按钮','Avatar Settings'=>'头像设置','You can select different comment thread layout for different comment forms in %s'=>'您可以为%s中的不同评论形式选择不同的评论主题布局','Comment Thread Layout #3'=>'评论线程布局#3','Comment Thread Layout #2'=>'评论线程布局#2','Comment Thread Layout #1'=>'评论线程布局#1','wpDiscuz 7 comes with three modern and totally different comment thread layouts. They are called Layout #1, Layout #2 and Layout #3.'=>'wpDiscuz 7带有三种现代且完全不同的评论线程布局。它们分别称为布局#1、布局#2和布局#3。','Here you can manage comment layout components. You can display/hide certain button or information on comment threads, as well as commenters\' avatars and comment voting options.'=>'您可在此管理评论布局组件。您可显示/隐藏评论线程上的某些按钮或信息，以及评论者的头像和评论投票选项。','Max number of comments'=>'最多评论数','Sitewide'=>'全站','Per Post'=>'每篇文章','Disable'=>'禁用','WordPress has already all necessary tools to moderate commends. You can approve, unapprove, mark as spam, delete and do other things with comments in WordPress Dashboard > Comments admin page. <br><br>On front-end you can only edit, close and stick comments. In case you want to have all moderation options on front-end, we recommend checkout %s addon. Besides the comment editing, closing and sticking options, here you can limit users commenting activity. You can set max number of comments per user per post or sitewide, allow them only comment or only reply.'=>'WordPress已经拥有所有必要的工具以进行评论审核。您可在WordPress仪表盘>评论管理页中批准、取消批准、将其标记为垃圾邮件、删除和执行其他操作。<br><br>在前端，您仅能编辑、关闭和置顶评论。若您想在前端使用所有审核选项，建议您查看%s插件。除了评论编辑、关闭和置顶选项之外，您还可在此处限制用户的评论活动。您可为每个用户或整个站点设置每位用户的最大评论数、仅允许他们评论或仅回复。','Show Follows Tab'=>'显示关注者标签','Show Subscriptions Tab'=>'显示订阅选项卡','Show Activity Tab'=>'展示活动选项卡','Enable button'=>'启用按钮','Here you can manage commenters authorization and data control related settings. wpDiscuz is focused on user engagement and community building ideas, therefore it\'s integrated with community builder plugins like wpForo Forum, BuddyPress, etc... With these plugins comment authors are linked to their profile pages. In case you want to display commenters profile and activity information directly on comment list, please be sure to check out the %s addon.'=>'在这您可管理评论者授权和与数据控制相关的设置。wpDiscuz专注于用户参与和社区建设思想，因此与wpForo论坛，BuddyPress等社区构建器插件集成在一起。通过这些插件，评论作者链接到其个人资料页面。若您想直接在评论列表中显示评论者资料和活动信息，请确保查看%s插件。','User Labels are small rectangles with specific background colors indicating comment author role, such as Guest, Member, Author, Admin, etc... These labels can be enabled and disabled for certain user role. Also you can change label colors using according options below.<br> Besides labels you can enable User Reputation, Badges and Ranks based on user activity, using %s addon. This addon integrates wpDiscuz comment system with an adaptive user points management plugin %s.'=>'用户标签是带有特定背景颜色的小矩形，用于指示评论者角色，如访客、成员、作者、管理员等。这些标签可为某些用户角色启用和禁用。您还可使用下列选项以更改标签颜色。<br>除了标签，您还可以使用%s插件根据用户活动启用用户信誉，徽章和等级。该插件将wpDiscuz评论系统与自适应用户点数管理插件%s集成在一起。','wpDiscuz allows users to get all kind of news from your website comment system, such as new comments, new replies, double opt-in subscription, user mentioning, user following and new comments by followed users. You can manage all those options here. All those options are based on email notifications. You can manage email templates in wpDiscuz > Phrases > Email Tab. <br>In wpDiscuz > Dashboard page, you can find a quick overview of user subscriptions. For an advanced subscriptions management tool, please checkout %s addon.'=>'wpDiscuz允许用户从您的网站评论系统中获取各种新闻，如新评论、新回复、双重选择订阅、用户提及、用户关注和关注用户的新评论。您可在此处管理所有这些选项。 所有这些选项均基于电子邮件通知。您可以在wpDiscuz>短语>电子邮件选项中管理邮件模板。<br>在wpDiscuz>仪表盘页，您可找到用户订阅的快速概述。要使用高级订阅管理工具，请查看%s插件。','Language codes'=>'语言代码','Example en'=>'例如en','Light'=>'浅色','reCAPTCHA V2 Secret Key'=>'reCAPTCHA V2 Secret Key','reCAPTCHA V2 Site Key'=>'reCAPTCHA V2 Site Key','reCAPTCHA v2'=>'reCAPTCHA v2','Post'=>'文章','CurlPost'=>'CurlPost','SocketPost'=>'SocketPost','Auto'=>'自动','If you want to use the latest Version 3 - Invisible Google reCAPTCHA with comment form, please checkout %s addon. This will make your commenters life easier, letting them pass through with ease.'=>'若您想使用最新V3-不可见的Google reCAPTCHA和评论表单，请查看%s插件。这将使您的评论者生活更轻松，让他们轻松通过。','reCAPTCHA Version 2'=>'reCAPTCHA V2','register your domain'=>'注册您的域名','Please %s with Google to obtain the Site Key and Secret Key for %s. Then insert those keys in according fields below.'=>'请%s与Google取得%s的Site Key和密钥。然后将这些密钥插入下面的字段中。','To start using Baidu Login Button you should get Client Id and Client Secret. Please follow to this '=>'要开始使用百度登录按钮，您应获取Client ID和Client Secret。请遵循此','To start using Tencent QQ Login Button you should get AppID and AppKey. Please follow to this '=>'要开始使用腾讯QQ登录按钮，您应该获取AppID和AppKey。请遵循此','Key'=>'Key','To start using Weibo Login Button you should get App Key and App Secret. Please follow to this '=>'要开始使用微博登录按钮，您应该获取App Key和App Secret。请遵循此','Secret'=>'Secret','To start using WeChat Login Button you should get AppID and Secret. Please follow to this '=>'要开始使用微信登录按钮，您应该获取AppID和Secret。请遵循此','Secret Key'=>'密钥','Password'=>'密码','ID'=>'ID','To start using Linkedin Login Button you should get Client ID and Client Secret. Please follow to this '=>'要开始使用Linkedin登录按钮，您应该获得Client ID和Client Secret。请遵循此','App Secret'=>'App Secret','App ID'=>'App ID','To start using Instagram Login Button you should get Client ID and Client Secret. Please follow to this '=>'要开始使用Instagram登录按钮，您应该获得Client ID和Client Secret。请遵循此','To start using Wordpress.com Login Button you should get Client ID and Client Secret. Please follow to this '=>'要开始使用Wordpress.com登录按钮，您应该获得Client ID和Client Secret。请遵循此','Public Key'=>'Public Key','To start using Disqus Login Button you should get Public Key and Secret Key. Please follow to this '=>'要开始使用Disqus登录按钮，您应该获得Public Key和Secret Key。请遵循此','Client Secret'=>'Client Secret','Permitted URI redirects'=>'允许URI重定向','wpDiscuz comes with built-in social login and share buttons. It includes Facebook, X, Google, Disqus, WordPress.com, VK and OK Social Networks. Here you can configure App IDs and Keys to enable those. Once IDs and Keys are configured you\'ll see social login buttons on top of the main comment form. Social Login buttons are only available for guests, so make sure you\'re logged-out before checking those.'=>'wpDiscuz内置了社交登录和分享按钮。它包括Facebook、X、Google、Disqus、WordPress.com、VK和OK社交网络。在这里，您可以配置应用程序ID和密钥以启用它们。配置ID和密钥后，您将在主评论表单顶部看到社交登录按钮。社交登录按钮仅适用于访客，因此请确保在查看这些按钮之前已注销。','Inline Feedback Icon Colors'=>'内联反馈图标颜色','Comment Bubble Colors'=>'评论气泡颜色','Here you can manage comment thread styles, custom colors and add custom CSS. By default wpDiscuz comes with &laquo;Light&raquo; style. If your theme style is dark, we recommend choose the &laquo;Dark&raquo; option for comments too. In case you want to totally customize comment style or create it from scratch, we recommend choose the &laquo;Off&raquo; option to stop loading wpDiscuz core CSS. In this case only basic CSS code will be loaded allowing you add your custom style easier.'=>'在这您可以管理评论线程样式、自定义颜色和添加自定义CSS。默认情况下，wpDiscuz带有&laquo;浅色&raquo;样式。若您的主题风格是深色的，我们建议您也选择&laquo;深色&raquo;选项进行评论；若您想完全自定义评论样式或从头开始创建评论样式，我们建议选择“关闭”选项以停止加载wpDiscuz核心CSS。在此情况下，将只加载基本CSS代码，允许您更轻松地添加自定义样式。','Height (px)'=>'高度 (px)','Width (px)'=>'宽度 (px)','Server \'post_max_size\' is '=>'服务器\'post_max_size\'为','Server \'upload_max_filesize\' is '=>'服务器\'upload_max_filesize\'为','Invert Selection'=>'取消选择','Unselect All'=>'取消全选','Select All'=>'全选','File Attachment Settings'=>'文件附件设置','Here you can manage comment content related options, such as comment text length, comment content breaking, comment image attachment... By default wpDiscuz allows to attach one image with comment. For an advanced media uploading and file attachment options we recommend %s addon.'=>'在此处您可管理与评论内容相关的选项，如评论文本长度、评论内容中断、评论图片附件...默认情况下，wpDiscuz允许附加一张带有评论的图片。对于高级媒体上传和文件附件选项，我们推荐%s插件。','Before Comment Form'=>'之前的评论表单','Comment Form Manager &raquo;'=>'评论表单管理&raquo;','The second type, is the old, comment depended way. You should create a "Rating" custom field in comment form allowing people to rate while they leave a comment. If you\'ve already configured the second type (Rating comment field) in comment form, the first type will be automatically disabled. Both types of ratings can be managed in %s'=>'第二种是基于评论的旧方法。您应该在评论表单中创建“评分”自定义字段，允许人们在发表评论时进行评分。若您已经在评论表单中配置了第二种类型（“评分评论”字段），则第一种类型将被自动禁用。两种类型的评分都可以在%s中进行管理','You have two ways to add Post Rating for your blog posts and articles. The first, comment independent type is enabled by default and appears on top of comment section. It allows people rate your articles without leaving comments. '=>'您可通过两种方式为博客文章和文章添加文章评级。默认情况下，第一种与评论无关的类型是启用的，并显示在评论区顶部。它使人们可对您的文章进行评分而不留下评论。','Go to "Comment Content and Media" admin page to manage image attachment settings'=>'转到“评论内容和媒体”管理页面以管理图像附件设置','Enable formatting toolbar'=>'启用格式工具栏','Disable formatting toolbar'=>'禁用格式工具栏','Source Code'=>'源代码','Link'=>'链接','Code Block'=>'代码块','Blockquote'=>'引用','Unordered List'=>'无序列表','Ordered List'=>'有序列表','Strike'=>'删除线','Underline'=>'下划线','Italic'=>'斜体','Bold'=>'粗体','Only Desktop'=>'仅桌面版','Mobile and Desktop'=>'移动版和桌面版','Comment Form Manager'=>'评论表单管理器','wpDiscuz allows you to customize comment form layout and fields. You can create as much comment forms as you want and attach those to certain post type or page. Please navigate to %s page to manage comment form specific settings.'=>'wpDiscuz允许您自定义评论表单的布局和字段。您可以根据需要创建任意数量的评论表单，并将其附加到某些帖子类型或页面。请导航到%s页面以管理评论表单的特定设置。','Media'=>'媒体','Allow Guests to Rate'=>'允许访客评分','Post Rating Title'=>'文章评分标题','Enable Post Rating'=>'启用文章评分','Layout'=>'布局','Comment List Layout'=>'评论列表布局','Theme'=>'主题','Comment form header text (plural)'=>'评论表单标题文本(复数)','Comment form header text (singular)'=>'评论表单标题文本(单数)','Average Rating'=>'平均评分','reCaptcha validation fails. Error code: '=>'reCaptcha验证失败。错误代码：','The response is no longer valid: either is too old or has been used previously.'=>'响应不再有效：太旧或曾经使用过。','The request is invalid or malformed.'=>'该请求无效或格式错误。','The response parameter is invalid or malformed.'=>'响应参数无效或格式错误。','The response parameter is missing.'=>'缺少响应参数。','The secret parameter is invalid or malformed.'=>'secret参数无效或格式错误。','The secret parameter is missing.'=>'secret参数丢失。','reCAPTCHA  verification failed.'=>'reCAPTCHA验证失败。','reCAPTCHA Settings'=>'reCAPTCHA设置','Name For Total'=>'总计名称','Google reCAPTCHA'=>'Google reCAPTCHA','Baidu authentication failed (access_token does not exist).'=>'百度认证失败（access_token不存在）','Baidu authentication failed (code does not exist).'=>'百度认证失败（代码不存在）','Baidu authentication failed (