n this?'=>'例如：对此有何想法？','A simple question or a call to leave a feedback on the selected part of text. Something like &quot;By the way. Do you agree with this?&quot; or &quot;Would love your thoughts, please comment on this.&quot;'=>'一个简单的问题或一个电话，在选定的文本部分留下反馈。比如&quot;顺便说一下。你同意吗？&quot;或者&quot;如果您愿意，请对此发表评论； ','Your Question to Readers'=>'给读者的问题','Selected Text'=>'所选文字','No text is selected. Please select a part of text from post content.'=>'未选择文本。请从文章内容中选择部分文字。','Do you really want to delet this attachment?'=>'您真的要删除此附件吗？','Do you really want to reset tab options?'=>'您真的要重置Tab选项吗？','Dashboard'=>'仪表盘','Unfollow'=>'取消关注','Something is wrong'=>'发生错误','Last Activity'=>'最近活动','Following'=>'正在关注','Subscription - comment'=>'订阅-评论','Subscription - all comments'=>'订阅-所有评论','Subscription - posts'=>'订阅-文章','Subscribers'=>'订阅者','Read More'=>'阅读更多','email for feedback'=>'反馈的电子邮件','I agree to receive email'=>'我同意接收电子邮件','If you want us to contact you please click on "I agree to receive email" checkbox, then fill out your email. We\'ll try to do our best to help you with problems.'=>'若您希望我们与您联系，请点击“我同意接收电子邮件”复选框，然后填写您的邮箱。我们将尽力为您解决问题。','Enter link:'=>'输入链接：','Reset Fields Ratings'=>'重置字段评分','Are you sure you want to reset fields ratings?'=>'您确定要重置字段评分吗？','Done'=>'完成','Working...'=>'工作中...','Reset Post Rating'=>'重置文章评分','Are you sure you want to reset post rating?'=>'您确定要重置文章评分吗？','Reset Ratings'=>'重置评分','Attached Images'=>'附加图片','gVectors Team'=>'gVectors团队','#1 WordPress Comment Plugin. Innovative, modern and feature-rich comment system to supercharge your website comment section.'=>'第一的WordPress评论插件。创新、现代且功能丰富的评论系统，可充实您网站的评论区。','Editor'=>'编辑','Hi [FOLLOWER_NAME],<br/><br/> new comment has been posted by the <em><strong>[COMMENT_AUTHOR]</em></strong> you are following<br/><br/><a href="[COMMENT_URL]">[COMMENT_URL]</a><br/><br/>[COMMENT_CONTENT]<br/><br/><a href="[CANCEL_URL]">'=>'[FOLLOWER_NAME]，您好<br/><br/> 您所关注的 <em><strong>[COMMENT_AUTHOR]</em></strong>已发表新评论<br/><br/><a href="[COMMENT_URL]">[COMMENT_URL]</a><br/><br/>[COMMENT_CONTENT]<br/><br/><a href="[CANCEL_URL]">','Hi, <br/> You just started following a new user. You\'ll get email notification once new comment is posted by this user. <br/> Please click on "user following confirmation" link to confirm your request. If you believe this is an error, ignore this message and we\'ll never bother you again. <br/><br/><a href="[POST_URL]">[POST_TITLE]</a><br/><br/><a href="[CONFIRM_URL]">'=>'您好，<br/>您刚开始关注一个新用户。一旦此用户发布了新的评论，您就会收到电子邮件通知。<br/>请点击“确认关注用户”按钮链接以确认您的请求。若您认为这是一个错误，请忽略此消息，我们将不再打扰您。<br/><br/><a href="[POST_URL]">[POST_TITLE]</a><br/><br/><a href="[CONFIRM_URL]">','Confirm Follow'=>'确认关注','Highlight Unread Comments'=>'高亮显示未读评论','By disabling this option you\'re automatically enabling wpDiscuz custom AJAX functions, which are many times faster that the default WordPress functions. Just make sure it doesn\'t conflict with your plugins.'=>'通过禁用此选项，将会自动启用wpDiscuz自定义AJAX函数，这比默认的WordPress函数快很多倍。您需确保它不会与您的其他插件冲突。','Use WordPress native AJAX functions'=>'使用WordPress原生AJAX函数','More Info &raquo;'=>'更多信息»','wpDiscuz Addons Bundle'=>'wpDiscuz扩展包','View wpDiscuz Addons Bundle'=>'查看wpDiscuz扩展包','All 16 addons in one bundle. Save 90% and get Unlimited Site License with one year premium support.'=>'全部16个扩展打包在一起。节省90%和获得无限的网站许可证与一年的优质支持。','Hi, <br/> You just subscribed for new comments on our website. This means you will receive an email when new comments are posted according to subscription option you\'ve chosen. <br/> To activate, click confirm below. If you believe this is an error, ignore this message and we\'ll never bother you again. <br/><br/><a href=\'[POST_URL]\'>[POST_TITLE]</a><br/><br/><a href=\'[CONFIRM_URL]\'>Confirm Your Subscription</a><br/><br/><a href=\'[CANCEL_URL]\'>Cancel Subscription</a>'=>'您好, <br/> 您刚在我们的网站上订阅了新评论。这意味着根据您选择的订阅选项发布新评论时，您将收到一封电子邮件。<br/>若要激活，请点击下面的“确认订阅”；若您认为这是一个错误，请忽略此消息，我们将不再打扰您。<br/><br/><a href=\'[POST_URL]\'>[POST_TITLE]</a><br/><br/><a href=\'[CONFIRM_URL]\'>确